name: Dating Factory

overview:
Dating Factory is a Swiss based white label dating provider offering a complete dating solution - from promoting other sites on the platform to creating a mainstream or niche dating site of your own and having other affiliates promote it for you.

Dating Factory platform was created in 2009 by former partners and affiliates of other white label dating networks to combine the marketing and industry knowledge and expertise with the most innovative technology and web 2.0 principles.

Main features that differ Dating Factory from other platforms:

1) International database, 10 languages available and growing 2) The ability to create the true niche dating sites 3) The most sophisticated SEO friendly sites layouts and usability 4) Advanced marketing and promotional tools. Marketing advice for partners 5) Total flexibility, full control over design and CSS 6) The ability to run your own affiliate network 7) Full in-depth reporting with all available parameters and traffic sources 8) No setup or maintenance costs, high revenue share for partners 9) Master partner franchise opportunities for the national markets
